River Plate             4:0       Rosario Central         
Vélez Sarsfield         6:0       Lanús                   
                
River Plate won the championship in this round with the following line-ups:

River Plate             Grisetti;
                        Vaghi, Ferreyra;
                        Yácono, Rossi, Ramos;
                        Reyes, Martínez, Di Stéfano, Labruna, Loustau.

Rosario Central         Quatrocchi;
                        Armándola, Soria;
                        Sosa, Castagno, Fogel;
                        Pérez, Santos, Zamaro, Vilariño, Valentini.

Referee                 Forte.

Att.                    18.000 tickets.

Field                   River Plate.

1-0 48' Di Stéfano.
2-0 50' Labruna.
3-0 62' Loustau.
4-0 89' Martínez.

